org.Spectrums

Class RTAligner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.Spectrums.RTAligner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class RTAligner
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class align two set of RT between observed data and library spectra. It will also automatically determine the RT tolerance window based on the observed data.
    Author:
    Jian
